'use client';

import Link from 'next/link';
import {
  Copy,
  EllipsisVertical,
  FileDown,
  FilePlus2,
  FileSearch2,
  FileUp,
  Pencil,
  Settings2,
  Trash2,
} from 'lucide-react';
import { Avatar, AvatarFallback, AvatarImage } from '@/components/ui/avatar';
import { Badge } from '@/components/ui/badge';
import { Button } from '@/components/ui/button';
import {
  Card,
  CardContent,
  CardFooter,
  CardHeader,
  CardHeading,
  CardTitle,
  CardToolbar,
} from '@/components/ui/card';
import {
  DropdownMenu,
  DropdownMenuContent,
  DropdownMenuItem,
  DropdownMenuPortal,
  DropdownMenuSeparator,
  DropdownMenuSub,
  DropdownMenuSubContent,
  DropdownMenuSubTrigger,
  DropdownMenuTrigger,
} from '@/components/ui/dropdown-menu';
import { Label } from '@/components/ui/label';
import { Switch } from '@/components/ui/switch';
import {
  Table,
  TableBody,
  TableCell,
  TableHead,
  TableHeader,
  TableRow,
} from '@/components/ui/table';

const items = [
  {
    avatar: '1.png',
    name: 'Tyler Hero',
    connections: 26,
    label: 'Project Member',
    joined: 'Today',
    disabled: true,
  },
  {
    avatar: '2.png',
    name: 'Esther Howard',
    connections: 639,
    label: 'Accountant',
    joined: '5 days ago',
    disabled: false,
  },
  {
    avatar: '3.png',
    name: 'Jacob Jones',
    connections: 125,
    label: 'Data Analyst',
    joined: '3 days ago',
    disabled: false,
  },
  {
    avatar: '4.png',
    name: 'Cody Fisher',
    connections: 81,
    label: 'Accountant',
    joined: '2 weeks ago',
    disabled: true,
  },
  {
    avatar: '5.png',
    name: 'Leslie Alexander',
    connections: 1203,
    label: 'Director',
    joined: '3 weeks ago',
    disabled: false,
  },
];

export default function Block() {
  return (
    <div className="flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen">
      <Card className="md:w-[800px]">
        <CardHeader>
          <CardHeading>
            <CardTitle>Members</CardTitle>
          </CardHeading>
          <CardToolbar>
            <div className="flex items-center space-x-2">
              <Label htmlFor="auto-update">Enforce 2FA</Label>
              <Switch id="auto-update" defaultChecked />
            </div>
            <DropdownMenu>
              <DropdownMenuTrigger asChild>
                <Button variant="ghost" size="sm">
                  <EllipsisVertical className="h-4 w-4" />
                </Button>
              </DropdownMenuTrigger>
              <DropdownMenuContent align="end">
                <DropdownMenuItem>
                  <FilePlus2 />
                  <Link href="#">Add</Link>
                </DropdownMenuItem>
                <DropdownMenuItem>
                  <FileDown />
                  <Link href="#">Import</Link>
                </DropdownMenuItem>
                <DropdownMenuSub>
                  <DropdownMenuSubTrigger>
                    <FileUp />
                    <span>Export</span>
                  </DropdownMenuSubTrigger>
                  <DropdownMenuPortal>
                    <DropdownMenuSubContent>
                      <DropdownMenuItem>
                        <span>PDF</span>
                      </DropdownMenuItem>
                      <DropdownMenuItem>
                        <span>CVG</span>
                      </DropdownMenuItem>
                      <DropdownMenuItem>
                        <span>Excel</span>
                      </DropdownMenuItem>
                    </DropdownMenuSubContent>
                  </DropdownMenuPortal>
                </DropdownMenuSub>
                <DropdownMenuItem>
                  <Settings2 />
                  <Link href="#">Settings</Link>
                </DropdownMenuItem>
              </DropdownMenuContent>
            </DropdownMenu>
          </CardToolbar>
        </CardHeader>
        <CardContent className="p-0">
          <Table>
            <TableHeader className="bg-muted">
              <TableRow>
                <TableHead>Name</TableHead>
                <TableHead>Role</TableHead>
                <TableHead>2FA</TableHead>
                <TableHead>Joined</TableHead>
                <TableHead></TableHead>
              </TableRow>
            </TableHeader>
            <TableBody>
              {items.map((item, index) => (
                <TableRow key={index}>
                  <TableCell>
                    <div className="flex items-center grow gap-2.5">
                      <Avatar className="size-9">
                        <AvatarImage
                          src={`/media/avatars/${item.avatar}`}
                          alt="@reui"
                        />
                        <AvatarFallback>CH</AvatarFallback>
                      </Avatar>
                      <div className="flex flex-col">
                        <Link
                          href="#"
                          className="text-sm font-semibold text-foreground hover:text-primary"
                        >
                          {item.name}
                        </Link>
                        <span className="text-xs font-normal text-muted-foreground">
                          {item.connections} connections
                        </span>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </TableCell>
                  <TableCell>
                    <Badge variant="secondary" appearance="outline">
                      {item.label}
                    </Badge>
                  </TableCell>
                  <TableCell>
                    <Badge
                      variant={item.disabled ? 'destructive' : 'success'}
                      appearance="outline"
                    >
                      {item.disabled ? 'Disabled' : 'Enabled'}
                    </Badge>
                  </TableCell>
                  <TableCell>{item.joined}</TableCell>
                  <TableCell className="flex justify-end">
                    <DropdownMenu>
                      <DropdownMenuTrigger asChild>
                        <Button variant="ghost" size="sm">
                          <EllipsisVertical className="h-4 w-4" />
                        </Button>
                      </DropdownMenuTrigger>
                      <DropdownMenuContent align="end">
                        <DropdownMenuItem>
                          <FileSearch2 />
                          <Link href="#">View</Link>
                        </DropdownMenuItem>
                        <DropdownMenuItem>
                          <FileUp />
                          <Link href="#">Export</Link>
                        </DropdownMenuItem>
                        <DropdownMenuSeparator />
                        <DropdownMenuItem>
                          <Pencil />
                          <Link href="#">Edit</Link>
                        </DropdownMenuItem>
                        <DropdownMenuItem>
                          <Copy />
                          <Link href="#">Make a copy</Link>
                        </DropdownMenuItem>
                        <DropdownMenuSeparator />
                        <DropdownMenuItem>
                          <Trash2 />
                          <Link href="#">Remove</Link>
                        </DropdownMenuItem>
                      </DropdownMenuContent>
                    </DropdownMenu>
                  </TableCell>
                </TableRow>
              ))}
            </TableBody>
          </Table>
        </CardContent>
        <CardFooter className="justify-center">
          <Button mode="link" underlined="dashed">
            <Link href="#">View 64 more</Link>
          </Button>
        </CardFooter>
      </Card>
    </div>
  );
}
